{"tid":2146635,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方將軍澳票控16名穿反光衣但非採訪或受僱傳媒人士","createTime":"2020-08-08T17:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T05:05:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"906c486be7c651f54185ca704804fbb916077655","tid":2146635,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F126401&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW1LtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=0eb9cf0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126401</a><br />\n<br />\n科大學生周梓樂離世9個月，網民昨晚號召到將軍澳悼念，警方在尚德邨票控16名並非進行傳媒採訪，或受僱於傳媒機構，但穿反光衣的人，涉嫌違反限聚令。警方說，昨晚7時許，多名穿反光背心的人在尚德邨外聚集，警方到場截停40多人，經調查後票控16人，其中7人是16歲以下未成年人士，最年輕的只有12歲。警方表示，近期越來越多穿著反光衣的人，在公眾活動出現，警員難以在短時間內識別身分，增加執法困難，譴責有人利用反光衣掩飾受禁群組聚集，又強調一直尊重記者採訪及新聞自由，在不影響行動的情況下，會盡量協調採訪工作。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-09 01:15:53"},{"pid":"2936a97e359451029a91ee8f07a27429997c0c3f","tid":2146635,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"党軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef481843ae46008d6125a74ad37a0693c95daee3","tid":2146635,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e6e463ce9fea535d594368f8eaa11ce44555e4","tid":2146635,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"